data.description: For sale by owner, with 2.5% commission to buyers agent. This beautiful 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage house could be yours! Built in 2003. It has been treated with excellent care and is in great condition. Great location, quiet neighborhood, and centrally located. Five minutes away from schools for all ages, five minutes from highway 429 to get you to downtown Orlando or the Turnpike. The house value will only increase with time, don't wait, inquire now.
